      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all seats are intact and functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely require routine maintenance soon, such as new tires and a brake service, to remain in top shape. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle perfect for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
