    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously kept, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
